data scientist
the data scientist is responsible for providing analytical horsepower to support key strategic and operational initiative based on established priority and a strong understanding of business strategy and process he or she frame and structure solution analyzes data and applies critical thinking in order to build advanced analytics model that add intelligence to business process or support business decision making a data scientist us analytical rigor and statistical method develops analysis and algorithm to research or mine through data and help advise on strategy and identify opportunity to optimize business operation product improvement and customer success
principal duties and responsibilities
act a an expert on the business' data including key data system and analysis platform that exist at autodesk
leverage technology including but not limited to sql python r sas spss strata tableau to collect process perform statistical data analysis and interpret result
data to be analyzed could include finance-related such a billing revenue subscription and entitlement subscription behavior such a renewal rate product usage purchasing licensing customer support resource capacity customer profile customer feedback web analytics marketing campaign etc
help create a data-driven culture by contributing to the development of the latest tool and capability
understand exiting metric and data model and make sure new research adheres to autodesk standard and add to the collective autodesk data infrastructure
ensures that new analysis are compared against standard or existing metric so that we do not deliver multiple different answer to the same question
clearly document provenance of data etl logic and code used to develop model
work with standard development tool like jira and git for managing work in an agile fashion and adding to the autodesk data infrastructure
work collaboratively and cross-functionally with sales engineering marketing finance operations legal and hr to define and meet stakeholder requirement
develop expertise in designated business area to provide deep dive analysis into metric trend and anomaly continually mining insight to drive product support and operational improvement
assess critical impact of business strategy and option and provide clear articulation of assessment to support decision making for senior management
analyze data and synthesize raw information into insight and recommendation
prepare presentation and clearly communicate finding from initiative to the broader organization
